Since 2011, Global Citizen has recorded over 19 million actions by supporters, who advocate for many different causes.
According to the organisation, these actions have helped to push global leaders to commit to and adopt policies worth more than $37 billion that are expected to change the lives of more than 2.25 billion people by 2030.
