After suffering a head injury, Christion Abercrombie underwent emergency surgery
Tennessee State's Christion Abercrombie, the Tennessee Tigers' second baseman, was rushed to emergency surgery after suffering a head injury Saturday in a 31-27 loss to the Vanderbilt Commodores.
